---
title: Roasted Chicken and Gravy with Pear and Chorizo Red Cabbage, Mushroom Stuffing, Roast Potatoes and Carrots
description: We love a good Roasted Chicken and Gravy and this deliciously simple, chef-curated recipe doesn't disappoint. Time to bust out the pots and pans!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/roasted-chicken-and-gravy-bf7a3880-2d485555.jpg
